remove the scrollbar
*********************

npm i react-remove-scroll-bar  --> install

import {RemoveScrollBar} from 'react-remove-scroll-bar';   --> import 

<div>

<RemoveScrollBar />

<div />
or

<RemoveScroll>
  Only this content would be scrollable
</RemoveScroll>




